Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.effects

Class NoStudentInfluenceStrategy

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.effects.NoStudentInfluenceStrategy
All Implemented Interfaces:
InfluenceStrategy
public class NoStudentInfluenceStrategy extends Object implements InfluenceStrategy
This class calculates the influence considering the fact that all students of a specific RealmType will not be considered during the influence calculation.
